BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 658 Td (Sophia was twelve when she realized she had been trying to be everyone else.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 643 Td (She copied her friend's style, laughed at jokes she did not find funny, and) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (pretended to like music she actually hated. One day her grandmother said) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (something that changed everything: 'Sophia, you are enough exactly as you) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 598 Td (are.' Those words unlocked something inside her.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 568 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 72 563 m 160 563 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 545 Td (You do not need to be prettier, smarter, funnier, or more popular to be worthy) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 530 Td (of love and respect. You are enough RIGHT NOW. Not when you lose weight. Not) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 515 Td (when you get better grades. Not when that popular girl finally notices you.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 500 Td (Right now, today, as you are reading this sentence.) Tj ET

