BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (something interesting happened: she looked at the winning projects and) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (realized what she could learn from them. The next year, she won first place.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 583 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 72 578 m 160 578 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 560 Td (Failure is not the opposite of success. It is the PATH to success. Every) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 545 Td (successful woman you admire has failed dozens, hundreds, maybe thousands of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 530 Td (times. The difference is that they got back up. They learned. They adjusted.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 515 Td (And they tried again. Failure does not mean you are not good enough. It means) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 500 Td (you are brave enough to try.) Tj ET

