q 0.4 G 1 w 72 676 m 160 676 l S Q
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 658 Td (Lily said yes to everything because she was afraid people would not like her) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 643 Td (if she said no. She was exhausted, overwhelmed, and resentful. She was on five) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (committees, helped everyone with homework, and never had time for herself.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (Learning to say no was the hardest and most important thing she ever did.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 583 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 72 578 m 160 578 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 560 Td (No is a complete sentence. You do not owe anyone an explanation for protecting) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 545 Td (your time, your energy, or your body. Saying no to things that drain you means) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 530 Td (saying YES to things that matter. People who respect you will respect your no.) Tj ET

endstream
