BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 515 Td (respond. You can refuse to shrink yourself. You can refuse to believe their) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 500 Td (words. And you can always ask for help from trusted adults.) Tj ET

